code: import axios from'axios';export const obtenerCliente=async()=>{const response=await axios.get('http://localhost:8000/cliente/api/v1/cliente/');return response.data;};export const crearCliente=async cliente=>{const response=await axios.post('http://localhost:8000/cliente/api/v1/cliente/',cliente);return response.data;};export const eliminarCliente=async id=>{const response=await axios.delete("http://localhost:8000/cliente/api/v1/cliente/".concat(id,"/"));return response.data;};export const actualizarCliente=async(id,cliente)=>{const response=await axios.put("http://localhost:8000/cliente/api/v1/cliente/".concat(id,"/"),cliente);return response.data;};
